173 A.3d 599 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DAREL ASHLEY A/K/A DARRELL D. ASHLEY, ANDRE D. ASHLEY, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-309 September Term 2017

079052 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004849-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
